content.description: Start from the ground, climb just left of large pine tree avoiding the splitter crack to the left.  Surmout ledge at midpoint then hug arete to top.
content.protection: TR...gear in the 2"-4" range and a 20' sling or two

content.description: Start on thin face moves,crappy feet and move up to overhang. Avoiding cracks on right and left. Climb past overhang to 20' of horizantal thin slopers.
content.protection: for toprope a few pieces in the 2-4" range and a couple of 20'+ slings.
content.location: Middle route on picnic face. obvious clean face eight feet left of twin spittercracks.
